 . The name is now in widespread and frequent use outside Wales, in many cases representing a transferred use of the surname so spelled, which is derived from the given name."]},{"name":"Rees","meanings":["Anglicized spelling of Welsh Rhys, in some cases representing a transferred use of the surname so spelled, which is derived from the Welsh given name."]}]},{"name":"ap","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Loving’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Rhys ap Gwyn was born about 1300, in Anglesey, Wales, United Kingdom as the son of Gwyn ap Heilyn. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"ABT    1300–":"umbes 1300–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1330–Male":"1330–Surnud","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","ABT    1300":"umbes 1300","1300":"1300","1330":"1330","1270":"1270","of,Talybolion cmt,Anglesey,Wales":"Anglesey, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT    1300–":"noin 1300–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1330–Male":"1330–Kuollut","1270–Male":"1270–Kuollut","ABT    1300":"noin 1300","1300":"1300","1330":"1330","1270":"1270","of,Talybolion cmt,Anglesey,Wales":"Anglesey, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT    1300–":"environ 1300–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1330–Male":"1330–Décédé","1270–Male":"1270–Décédé","ABT    1300":"environ 1300","1300":"1300","1330":"1330","1270":"1270","of,Talybolion cmt,Anglesey,Wales":"Anglesey, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Rhys ap Gwyn est né environ 1300, à Anglesey, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni, fils de Gwyn ap Heilyn. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"ABT    1300–":"um 1300–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1330–Male":"1330–Verstorben","1270–Male":"1270–Verstorben","ABT    1300":"um 1300","1300":"1300","1330":"1330","1270":"1270","of,Talybolion cmt,Anglesey,Wales":"Anglesey, Wales, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Rhys ap Gwyn wurde um 1300 in Anglesey, Wales, United Kingdom, als Sohn von Gwyn ap Heilyn geboren. Er hatte mindesten